<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='498000' id='t-498000'>Sentinel lymph node dissection</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='500000' id='t-500000'>has really changed the way that we manage breast cancer, melanoma.</span>
